description: The only thing I like about the winter is the Christmas time. Especially the Christmas markets which are very popular here in the Czech Republic. You are likely to find me there almost every second day. But obviously many cute guys like those markets as well. Therefore I would never go there without my camcorder. And indeed the boys there today were amazing. Well, it still took me several tries but nonetheless I was successful. One very cute boy with a heavenly smile frankly told me that he "could do lots" for some extra cash. But would he be willing to sacrifice his virginity for my immoral offers?
title: Czech Hunter 68
